snippet.title: Supersolar Teaser #1
snippet.description:
Supersolar is a top-down action game with a one of a kind ship, dozens of weapons and various gear to use against crazy cool enemies like robot space squids and swarms of AI drones. 

We have vast and detailed levels to explore, and everything is packed in a story-driven single player campaign with realistic 3D graphics.

Website: http://supersolargame.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/supersolargame
IndieDB: https://www.indiedb.com/games/supersolar
